divs: Sighting Detailswe lived in apartments niebor dan told me someone was in our pool we ran them off before we could see them we were talking about it when three orb looking objectsfloated right past me towards dan i was thinking this is strange but did not say a word it was like a totalcalm came over me like it was alright for them to be there the orbs floated to the ground near the woods two weeks i ask dan if he had seen what i saw that night he said he did but thought it wasjust him isaid do you think anyone would belive us if we told them he said they would laugh at us if we said something about it
Summary: Yellow/green floated orbs about 2 feet wide.
